# 🎬 Netflix Content Analytics Dashboard

## 📌 Project Overview
This project analyzes the Netflix Content Library using Power BI. The dataset was cleaned and transformed using Python (Pandas) and Power Query before creating an interactive dashboard. The dashboard provides business insights into Netflix content based on countries, directors, genres, ratings, content type, and release years.

## 🛠️ Tools & Technologies
- Python
- Pandas
- Power BI
- Power Query
- DAX

## 📊 Dashboard Features
- KPI Cards
- Top 5 Countries by Content
- Content by Country and Type
- Content Released Over Time
- Content by Rating
- Top 10 Content Categories (Genres)
- Top Directors by Content
- Interactive Slicers

## 📈 Key Performance Indicators (KPIs)
- Total Content
- Total Movies
- Total TV Shows
- Total Directors
- Total Countries
- Total Rating Categories

## 💡 Business Insights
- The United States contributes the highest number of Netflix titles.
- Movies make up a larger portion of the content library than TV Shows.
- TV-MA is the most common content rating.
- Netflix's content library has grown significantly after 2015.
- Drama and Comedy are among the most popular content categories.

